# `astro.config.mjs` and `src/content.config.ts`

- **Change together when needed:** Content schema edits require checks across `src/pages/**` and any components reading `getCollection` data. Integration or `site` URL changes can affect `@astrojs/sitemap` and `rss.xml.js` (`context.site`).
- **`astro.config.mjs`:** Integrations are `sitemap()` and `mdx()`; Tailwind is via `@tailwindcss/vite` in `vite.plugins`. Do not assume extra integrations exist.
- **`src/content.config.ts`:** Uses `defineCollection`, `glob` loader, and `z` from `astro/zod`. Preserve `image()` usage for `team`, `work`, and `posts` image objects.
